              <circle cx="18" cy="8" r="5" fill="url(#grad3)"/>
              <!-- Dragon eye -->
              <circle cx="16" cy="7" r="1.5" fill="white"/>
              <circle cx="16" cy="7" r="0.8" fill="#1E293B"/>
              <!-- Dragon horn -->
              <path d="M20 4 L24 0 L22 6 Z" fill="#F59E0B"/>
              <!-- Dragon tail curl -->
              <path d="M18 32 C22 36 18 42 12 40" stroke="url(#grad3)" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <!-- Small flame -->
              <path d="M12 6 C10 4 8 6 10 8 C8 8 10 12 12 10" fill="#F59E0B"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Option 3: Guardian Dragon</h3>
          <p>A dragon protectively wrapped around a tooth. Conveys protection and care - great for trust-building.</p>
          <div class="logo-with-text">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
              <defs><linearGradient id="grad3b" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#D97706"/><stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#92400E"/></linearGradient></defs>
              <path d="M24 4 C18 4 14 10 14 16 C14 20 16 24 18 28 L20 42 L24 38 L28 42 L30 28 C32 24 34 20 34 16 C34 10 30 4 24 4 Z" fill="white" stroke="#E5E7EB" stroke-width="1"/>
              <path d="M8 20 C6 14 10 8 18 8 C14 12 12 18 14 24 C10 22 8 26 10 30 C6 32 8 38 14 38 C12 34 14 30 18 32" stroke="url(#grad3b)" stroke-width="4" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="18" cy="8" r="5" fill="url(#grad3b)"/>
              <circle cx="16" cy="7" r="1.5" fill="white"/>
              <circle cx="16" cy="7" r="0.8" fill="#1E293B"/>
              <path d="M20 4 L24 0 L22 6 Z" fill="#F59E0B"/>
              <path d="M18 32 C22 36 18 42 12 40" stroke="url(#grad3b)" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M12 6 C10 4 8 6 10 8 C8 8 10 12 12 10" fill="#F59E0B"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="logo-text-preview">Dental<span>ogix</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Option 4: Modern Dragon Shield -->
        <div class="logo-option-card" onclick="selectLogo(4)">
          <div class="logo-preview">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" class="logo-svg">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="grad4" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                  <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#D97706"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#92400E"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <linearGradient id="grad4light" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                  <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#FEF3C7"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#FDE68A"/>
                </linearGradient>
              </defs>
              <!-- Shield shape -->
              <path d="M24 2 L42 10 L42 26 C42 36 34 44 24 46 C14 44 6 36 6 26 L6 10 Z" fill="url(#grad4)"/>
              <!-- Inner shield highlight -->
              <path d="M24 6 L38 12 L38 26 C38 34 32 40 24 42 C16 40 10 34 10 26 L10 12 Z" fill="url(#grad4light)"/>
              <!-- Stylized dragon head profile -->
              <path d="M16 18 C16 14 20 12 24 14 L32 14 C34 14 36 16 34 18 L30 22 C32 24 32 28 30 30 L24 32 C20 32 18 28 20 24 L16 22 C14 20 14 18 16 18 Z" fill="url(#grad4)"/>
              <!-- Dragon eye -->
              <circle cx="22" cy="18" r="2" fill="white"/>
              <circle cx="22.5" cy="18" r="1" fill="#1E293B"/>
              <!-- Tooth in center -->
              <path d="M24 24 L22 28 L24 34 L26 28 Z" fill="white"/>
              <!-- Dragon nostril -->
              <circle cx="28" cy="20" r="1" fill="#78350F"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Option 4: Dragon Shield</h3>
          <p>A dragon profile inside a shield with a tooth. Conveys strength and protection - professional and bold.</p>
          <div class="logo-with-text">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
              <defs><linearGradient id="grad4b" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#D97706"/><stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#92400E"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="grad4lightb" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#FEF3C7"/><stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#FDE68A"/></linearGradient></defs>
              <path d="M24 2 L42 10 L42 26 C42 36 34 44 24 46 C14 44 6 36 6 26 L6 10 Z" fill="url(#grad4b)"/>
              <path d="M24 6 L38 12 L38 26 C38 34 32 40 24 42 C16 40 10 34 10 26 L10 12 Z" fill="url(#grad4lightb)"/>
              <path d="M16 18 C16 14 20 12 24 14 L32 14 C34 14 36 16 34 18 L30 22 C32 24 32 28 30 30 L24 32 C20 32 18 28 20 24 L16 22 C14 20 14 18 16 18 Z" fill="url(#grad4b)"/>
              <circle cx="22" cy="18" r="2" fill="white"/>
              <circle cx="22.5" cy="18" r="1" fill="#1E293B"/>
              <path d="M24 24 L22 28 L24 34 L26 28 Z" fill="white"/>
              <circle cx="28" cy="20" r="1" fill="#78350F"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="logo-text-preview">Dental<span>ogix</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="logo-selection-info">
        <p>Let me know which option you prefer (1, 2, 3, or 4) and I'll update the website with that logo!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
.logo-options-section {
  padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
}

.logo-options-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-2xl);
}

.logo-option-card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  padding: var(--space-2xl);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all var(--transition-base);
  border: 3px solid transparent;
}

.logo-option-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

.logo-preview {
  background: var(--color-gray-50);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-2xl);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.logo-svg {
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
}

.logo-option-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  color: var(--color-gray-900);
}

.logo-option-card p {
  color: var(--color-gray-600);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.logo-with-text {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-md);
  padding: var(--space-md);
  background: var(--color-gray-100);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}

.logo-text-preview {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-gray-900);
}

.logo-text-preview span {
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.logo-selection-info {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: var(--color-accent-soft);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
}

.logo-selection-info p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--color-gray-700);
}
</style>

